  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Marketing Associate",
  "description": "<h2>🌟 Marketing Associate</h2><p>✨ Want a role where you <em>learn by doing</em> and actually see your progress?</p><p>At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, you’ll be part of on-ground marketing campaigns where you meet people, represent brands, and build real-life communication and sales skills. No boring desk routine — just hands-on experience and steady growth.</p><h2>💼 What You’ll Be Doing</h2><p>🤝 Chat with customers through friendly, face-to-face interactions<br />📣 Share and explain client offerings in a clear, professional way<br />📈 Pick up marketing & sales skills through real-world experience<br />👥 Work alongside a supportive team at events, campaigns, and outreach activities</p><h2>🚀 What You’ll Get</h2><p>🎓 Full training provided — no experience needed<br />📊 Performance-based growth with clear progression paths<br />🌍 Opportunities to take part in different campaigns and locations<br />🤝 Coaching, guidance, and continuous support from the team</p><h2>🙌 This Role Is Great For You If You</h2><p>✔️ Enjoy meeting and talking to people<br />✔️ Are motivated and open to learning<br />✔️ Welcome feedback and personal growth<br />✔️ Prefer active, on-the-ground work over desk-based roles</p><h2>📩 How to Apply</h2><p>If you’re keen to build hands-on experience in marketing and customer engagement, we’d love to connect.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507</p>",
